{
  "text": "3) Healthy control subjects. HLA genotypes from 621 adult white U.K. control subjects with no history of autoimmune disease were provided by Steven Gough (Institute of Biomedical Research, University of Birmingham, Birmingham, U.K.) and have been described previously [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "42302124"
